	(mod25519_reduce): Remove a call to memcpy.  Use bn256_add_uint.
	* src/ecc-edwards.c (point_double): Simplify.

2014-04-16  Niibe Yutaka  <gniibe@fsij.org>

	* VERSION: 1.1.3.

