	* regnual/regnual.ld (.bss): Put at RAM1.  This makes reGNUal can
	be loaded on the lower address.

	* regnual/sys.c (entry): Don't change SP.  Put alignment.

	* regnual/regnual.c (usb_cb_get_descriptor): Fix adding break.

